Web Chat Troubleshooting If webchat interactions are not being routed to the correct agent/queue or are not appearing in the interaction pane, please walk through the following troubleshooting tips:
  Confirm agent is a member of the queue that was created at the beginning of the workshop
  Confirm you are using widget version &ldquo;V1&rdquo;
  Confirm agent status is set to &ldquo;On-Queue&rdquo;
  If interactions are still not being routed correctly, please reach out to Veronica Guevara at veronica.guevara@genesys.com.
